<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Hopton 10k - A multi-terrain road and trail race in Hopton, West Yorkshire on Hopton 10k road and trail running race, Mirfield, West Yorkshire</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/</link><description>Recent content in Hopton 10k - A multi-terrain road and trail race in Hopton, West Yorkshire on Hopton 10k road and trail running race, Mirfield, West Yorkshire</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-gb</language><lastBuildDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2019 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://hopton10k.run/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Planning</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/blog/2019/07/08/planning/</link><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/blog/2019/07/08/planning/</guid><description>Plans are coming along well, all systems go.</description></item><item><title>Walking the route</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/blog/2019/07/07/recce/</link><pubDate>Sun, 07 Jul 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/blog/2019/07/07/recce/</guid><description>I carried out a recce of the route with the family today. It showed me that this route is both great fun, but challenging in places&amp;hellip;</description></item><item><title>Volunteers needed</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/blog/2019/06/24/become-a-volunteer/</link><pubDate>Mon, 24 Jun 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/blog/2019/06/24/become-a-volunteer/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="become-a-volunteer"&gt;Become a volunteer&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Love getting up early?&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Contact Us</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/contact/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/contact/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="get-in-touch"&gt;Get in Touch&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have a question about the Hopton 10k? We&amp;rsquo;d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="before-you-contact-us"&gt;Before You Contact Us&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You might find your answer in our:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://hopton10k.run/faq/"&gt;FAQ page&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; — questions about entering, eligibility, and what&amp;rsquo;s included&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://hopton10k.run/raceday/"&gt;Race Day page&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; — parking, registration, route, and logistics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-reach-us"&gt;How to Reach Us&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="email"&gt;Email&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="mailto:info@hopton10k.run"&gt;info@hopton10k.run&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We aim to respond within 48 hours. During race week, we may be a little slower!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Donate</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/donate/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/donate/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;script&gt;
 window.location = 'https://www.justgiving.com/crowdfunding/hopton10k';
&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;h3 id="make-a-donation"&gt;Make a donation&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To support our school and all the parents and teachers who are taking part in the Hopton 10k, please visit our &lt;a href="https://www.justgiving.com/crowdfunding/hopton10k"&gt;Just Giving page&lt;/a&gt; to donate. Your support is greatly appreciated.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="donate-now"&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.justgiving.com/crowdfunding/hopton10k"&gt;Donate Now&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;</description></item><item><title>Frequently Asked Questions</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/faq/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/faq/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Got questions about entering the Hopton 10k? Find answers below. For race day specific information (parking, check-in, route details), see our &lt;a href="https://hopton10k.run/raceday/"&gt;Race Day&lt;/a&gt; page.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="about-the-race"&gt;About the Race&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="when-is-the-race"&gt;When is the race?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sunday 27th September 2026 at 10am&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Hopton 10k takes place on the first Sunday in October (or late September) every year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="where-does-the-race-start"&gt;Where does the race start?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The race starts and finishes at &lt;a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Hopton+Primary+School/@53.6721243,-1.6999666,15z"&gt;Hopton Primary School&lt;/a&gt;, Woodend Road, Mirfield, WF14 8PR. From there, the route heads through Lower Hopton before entering the beautiful woodland trails.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 1 - Chadwick Lane</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m1/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m1/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 10 - Sands Lane, Left to Lady</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m10/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m10/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 11 - Lady Woods bottom</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m11/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m11/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 12 - Lady Woods go straight</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m12/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m12/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 13 - Exit via stile</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m13/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m13/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 14 - Ex-Paradise Farm</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m14/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m14/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 15 - Ouzelwell Water</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m15/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m15/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 16 - Ouzelwell Farm</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m16/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m16/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 17 - Ouzelwell Top</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m17/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m17/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 18 - The Bog</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m18/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m18/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 19 - Don't go down there!</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m19/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m19/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 2 - Flowerpot junction</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m2/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m2/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 20 - Yes, DO go down there</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m20/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m20/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 3 - Granny Lane</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m3/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m3/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 4 - Hagg Lane Junction</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m4/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m4/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 5 - Hagg Lane / Boathouse</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m5/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m5/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 6 - Hagg Woods Crossroads</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m6/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m6/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 7 - Golf course Bottom</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m7/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m7/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 8 - Golf course Top</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m8/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m8/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://goo.gl/maps/4YtAR3n756Ga5p6DA"&gt;https://goo.gl/maps/4YtAR3n756Ga5p6DA&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Marshal Point 9 - Sands Lane</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/m9/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/m9/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Race Day Information</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/raceday/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/raceday/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Everything you need to know to make your race day run smoothly. For general questions about entering, see our &lt;a href="https://hopton10k.run/faq/"&gt;FAQ page&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="key-times"&gt;Key Times&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
 &lt;thead&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Time&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;th&gt;Activity&lt;/th&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/thead&gt;
 &lt;tbody&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8:45am&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Registration opens&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9:50am&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Registration closes&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10:00am&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Race starts&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;tr&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;11:30am&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;td&gt;Course cut-off (marshals pack up)&lt;/td&gt;
 &lt;/tr&gt;
 &lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="getting-there"&gt;Getting There&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="location"&gt;Location&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The race starts and finishes at &lt;strong&gt;Hopton Primary School&lt;/strong&gt;, Woodend Road, Mirfield, WF14 8PR.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Important:&lt;/strong&gt; Enter the school grounds through the &lt;strong&gt;playground gate on Chadwick Lane&lt;/strong&gt;. The main entrance and front gates will not be open.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Race Results</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/results/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/results/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="hopton-10k-results"&gt;Hopton 10k Results&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Since our first race in 2019, the Hopton 10k has welcomed hundreds of runners to tackle our challenging course. Below you&amp;rsquo;ll find the winners from each year along with links to the full results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Looking for your time?&lt;/strong&gt; Full results are published on &lt;a href="https://racebest.com/results/"&gt;RaceBest&lt;/a&gt; shortly after each race finishes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h2 id="2025"&gt;2025&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="row"&gt;
&lt;div class="col-md-6"&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;i class="fa fa-male"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Male Winner&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Adam Thompson&lt;/strong&gt; (Stockport Harriers &amp; AC)&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="text-muted"&gt;40:38&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class="col-md-6"&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;i class="fa fa-female"&gt;&lt;/i&gt; Female Winner&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ciara Ellis&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class="text-muted"&gt;47:14&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Sponsorship Opportunities</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/sponsorship/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/sponsorship/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="partner-with-the-hopton-10k"&gt;Partner with the Hopton 10k&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Looking for a unique opportunity to connect with hundreds of active, community-minded people in West Yorkshire? The Hopton 10k offers excellent visibility for local and national businesses alike.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All sponsorship funds go directly to supporting Hopton Primary School. To discuss options, use the contact form below or email &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="mailto:info@hopton10k.run"&gt;info@hopton10k.run&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="package-1-platinum-sponsor-800--1-package-available"&gt;Package 1: Platinum sponsor (£800) – 1 package available&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In return for your support as platinum sponsor, Hopton 10k would provide:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Volunteer with Us</title><link>https://hopton10k.run/volunteers/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://hopton10k.run/volunteers/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;type = &amp;ldquo;page&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="be-part-of-the-team"&gt;Be Part of the Team&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Hopton 10k wouldn&amp;rsquo;t happen without our amazing volunteers. We need around &lt;strong&gt;40 people&lt;/strong&gt; to run the race safely, and we&amp;rsquo;re proud to have the friendliest marshals and helpers around.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s in it for you?&lt;/strong&gt; A free T-shirt, goody bag, plenty of tea and coffee, and the satisfaction of cheering runners home. It&amp;rsquo;s a great morning out!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Interested? Email us at &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="mailto:info@hopton10k.run"&gt;info@hopton10k.run&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt; or fill in the contact form at the bottom of this page.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>